title: ESRI Community Topographic Basemap
name: ESRI Community Topographic Basemap
description:
This map presents a tour of the community basemaps that have been developed by ESRI and other ArcGIS users as part of the Community Maps Program.  The map features three basemaps:



World Imagery
World Street Map
World Topographic Map
These are multi-scale basemaps that are designed for overlaying other layers of geographic information.  You can choose between these basemaps for the type of information you are intending to display.  The basemaps have been built from a variety of best available data from many different governmental and commercial organizations.
